{"tid":1266283,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"BBC: 因媒體報道，並在社交媒體上被廣為流傳討論而產生的「傳染效應」也可能是原因之一。","createTime":"2019-06-29T13:36:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T17:51:50.000Z","uid":73621,"like":50,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"dc7ad932e3bc06a4313261c356dd1982670c806f","tid":1266283,"uid":73621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T13:36:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/china/2016/03/160318_ana_hong_kong_youth_suicide\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchina%2F2016%2F03%2F160318_ana_hong_kong_youth_suicide&d=raogrMnRIgwaKnbVZhVJo4c%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=f5e00d1d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchina%2F2016%2F03%2F160318_ana_hong_kong_youth_suicide&h=ec6188df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/china/2016/03/160318_ana_hong_kong_youth_suicide</a><br />\n<br />\n自殺訊息會在年輕人之中流傳，社交媒體扮演了關鍵的角色，而有些過於具體的描述自殺方式，或是將自殺者死因過度簡化歸類的報道，可能影響心理狀態比較脆弱的人，產生模仿效應。網絡上對於自殺新聞的評論留言，有時也令人難以承受。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請停止回應D放負、渲染自殺post<br />\n係網絡發表言論可以係好不負責任<br />\n但如果真心為大家好<br />\n請勿突然話好灰、想自殺<br />\n幫手推下<br />\n<br />\n懷疑部分會員故意渲染自殺氣氛<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1266120\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1266120</a><br />\n<br />\n[非帶風向] 想回應一下 林 日 曦 引述cctvb記者朋友的文章<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1265764\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1265764</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"769a6e75fbde177340935796a8c331d97e3132e8","tid":1266283,"uid":132128,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T13:37:48.000Z","msg":"日日都mon住連登<br />\n真係好撚辛苦"},{"pid":"f8fe682a8c3f7a49b06039c437acaf48bc00f953","tid":1266283,"uid":26333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T13:38:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e349b32e5d42d57eafc5c9f9e59